    "subtitle": "How do you relate to past, present, and future? Five time orientations, none of them the \"right\" one.",
    "description": "<p>This is not about balance versus imbalance — different time orientations serve different life phases. It shows which orientations currently dominate you, so you can tell whether your time horizon is chosen or just inherited.</p><p>Inspired by Zimbardo Time Perspective concepts. Items are original (ZTPI is copyrighted and not reproduced).</p>",
