    "privacyNote": "Your answers stay in this browser. The result belongs to you. Sharing is your choice.",
    "disclaimer": "Inspired by Zimbardo Time Perspective concepts. Items are original. This is not the validated ZTPI and not a clinical assessment.",
    "startButton": "Frame my time horizon"
  },
